{
  "chapter": 52,
  "chapter_summary": "第五十二回 葫芦岛\n\n本章讲述了芮玮、玉面神婆、叶青、简怀萱、呼哈娜五人在海上的遭遇。欧阳龙年以芮玮为人质，要求叶青用解药交换其子欧阳波。玉面神婆与欧阳龙年斗智斗勇，最终达成交换协议。众人乘坐小船离开大船，玉面神婆提前准备了桨和食物。途中，芮玮询问玉面神婆关于牛毛天王针的传承，得知其弟子刘育芷一直在暗中关注他们。众人发现一座形似葫芦的小岛，玉面神婆兴奋地表示岛上住着胡一刀的师父，但这位高人已经去世。本章展现了江湖人物的恩怨情仇，以及玉面神婆的机智和丰富经验。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "text": "老巫婆，杖法大有长进啊！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "丫头快将我儿子醒转！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "text": "咱们交换如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "如何交换？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "text": "那丫头醒转吾儿，老夫就放芮玮随你们去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "text": "而且老夫收回不准芮玮再上任何船的话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "好，你放开大哥，我就醒转令郎。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "你先醒转吾儿。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "且慢！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "text": "蒋婆子，你是存心跟我过不去吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "等那老糊涂先放开芮玮，咱们再醒转他的宝贝儿子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "text": "老巫婆，我先想不再逼你随她们坐小船离去，心想你只要和和气气留下，我一定不为难你，哪知你处处与我为难，别再想留在老夫船上！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "老身早就不预备再留你这船上。你就是留我，老身还不愿意，别再啰嗦，放下芮玮，咱们拍手就走。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "text": "你想诳我吗？先醒转我儿子再说。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "姑娘，淫徒交给我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "你们先下船等着，这里有我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "听老前辈的吩咐，先下船去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "老糊涂咱们交换吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "text": "怎么换法？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "咱们发誓不准弄鬼，你交给我，我交给你，两不吃亏。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "text": "不成，我儿子昏迷不知人事，你叫那丫头先醒转吾儿，咱们再交换。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "她将你儿子弄昏自有解药，可是解药不能交给你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "text": "不交给我，老夫不但将这臭小子杀掉，还要你们三人活活淹死海中赔上一命，谅你们逃不出老夫的掌心。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "就是怕你来那招活活淹死，不错，咱们船逃不出你的掌心，你只要冲上，咱们经不起一冲，小船就要被大船冲翻，岂不泡在海中活活淹死？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "text": "蒋婆子，你也怕我啊！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "老糊涂怎么说？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "speaker_name": "欧阳龙年",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "text": "那只小船无桨无桅，你们坐上去迟早要死，犯不着将你们冲翻落个害人的罪名，只要解药交来，我的船立刻驰离此地，决不加害你们。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_ou_yang_long_nian",
      "text": "就这么说定？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "姑娘，解药抛上来。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "text": "咱们无桨无桅怎么走啊？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "text": "桨是有的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "text": "哪儿来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "text": "在你们与歹徒说话的当儿，从大船另旁舱门取出这桨及食水、食物，尽可飘荡一月。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "text": "老前辈行动恁的快，真是神人！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥、青姐，我以为再也见不到你们了，幸亏抱着船桅飘流被大船救起，这恩惠我终身不忘。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "说来欧阳父子将老身救起亦有恩惠，可惜欧阳龙年的儿子大大不肖，将那恩惠勾销得一丝不存。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "text": "没想到欧阳老先生的儿子那么坏，我一急之下跳到海中，若不是老前辈暗中救起，还是与波浪为伍。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "欧阳老儿不是坏人，就是不会管儿子！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "text": "他大儿子被谁杀的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "七大剑派的掌门人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "text": "欧阳前辈觅得七大剑派的掌门人一一杀死，替儿复仇！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "就因此故，海龙王得罪天下武林正义道，他也自知不该，消声匿迹，再也不走动江湖。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "text": "他那大儿子到底犯何罪行，惹起七大掌门联合起来杀他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "所行罪恶数不胜数，而且那大儿子尽得欧阳龙年武功真传，一时江湖无人制住得了，要不是七大掌门联手杀掉，还不知让他们多行多少坏事，唉！欧阳龙年终身英名就坏在儿子身上，如今这儿子又是个大坏蛋，还好欧阳龙年没有传出武功的精华，就是将来为害江湖，不会像他兄长一般犯罪累累，横行一世。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "这样划，总有一日会到陆地，中原在南面，运气好会划到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "运气不好呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "南方岛屿多，运气不好，一月内也能踏上一个岛屿，咱们在岛上换上食水、食物就可再划。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_ye_qing",
      "text": "如此一来，不怕回不到中原了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "text": "老前辈有没有徒弟？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你怎会突问这句话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "text": "闻说天山玉面神婆从不收徒，但是老前辈的独门绝技牛毛天王针也有一人会，实令晚辈疑惑，是故问了出来，莫非另有人会前辈的牛毛天王针吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不，天下只有两人会牛毛天王针这门技艺，一个是我，一个是我惟一的弟子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "text": "前辈弟子可是女的，名叫刘育芷？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "text": "刘姐姐，不错，我听刘姐姐说过牛毛天王针。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我本不收徒，结果还是收了刘育芷，其中有段因果，这次来到海上，我那徒儿还托我一事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "她说有位姓芮的青年带她夫家的妹妹至魔鬼岛治病，她不便跟随，又不放心，恰好老身要来海中寻个小岛，顺便替她注意。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "text": "刘姐姐真好，一直关心我。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "speaker_name": "简怀萱",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥，你看那小岛好像个葫芦啊？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_jian_huai_xuan",
      "text": "真像个葫芦吗？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_qing",
      "speaker_name": "叶青",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "text": "像，像极了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_ha_na",
      "speaker_name": "呼哈娜",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "text": "像，像极了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "快划，快划……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "糊涂！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "text": "老前辈，岛上有什么令你如此兴奋？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "上面住着一位高人，是胡一刀的师父。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "text": "胡一刀的师父！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "text": "胡一刀的师父怕有一百多岁了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "至少一百五十岁了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "text": "还活着吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_mian_shen_po",
      "speaker_name": "玉面神婆",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不，老早死了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 52,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    }
  ],
